{"tid":1951113,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我以為已經放低咗 但好似從來都無放低過","createTime":"2020-03-30T18:55:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T21:06:32.000Z","uid":242600,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2b1a2127b3d8e56274f5be3c5d0346f4afd65b60","tid":1951113,"uid":242600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T18:55:26.000Z","msg":"我暗戀一個男仔4年，因為某啲原因令佢知我鍾意過佢<br />\n一直以來都係我單方面嘅明戀暗戀，我曾經覺得有啲攰，所以想放棄<br />\n當時我以為自己放棄咗，所以我之後都有留意其他男仔<br />\n但時至今日，由想放棄佢開始已經過咗差唔多4年<br />\n我發現我始終都係放唔低佢，到底我應該點做？"},{"pid":"27a7d5058419dd3670fe5653c651e24a1606bb91","tid":1951113,"uid":352408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T18:59:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f9f008f19b70b17b1f122576579d6c15074a395","tid":1951113,"uid":305287,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T19:07:51.000Z","msg":"你生活多唔多接觸男仔？ 有冇試過拍拖？<br />\n個男仔可能係好好 但已經4年啦 你中意嘅係回憶 佢都變曬啦 同到佢一齊都唔會係你中意個個佢 試下識下其他仔 玩下交友app 會發現個世界好大 加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"740d1f8694265f8af7a460472d04013bf69f57af","tid":1951113,"uid":210165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T19:08:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6f829b2a131d8759be81bfa2f2b699dfc872fe28","tid":1951113,"uid":166996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T19:13:39.000Z","msg":"Same...絲打堅強 搵其他目標分下心"},{"pid":"2025b47ad9907f1d908eef4dfd44c5a58eaed26c","tid":1951113,"uid":158741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T19:23:17.000Z","msg":"其實4 年 個男仔係咪已經變咗性格 唔再係4年前你鐘意個個人"},{"pid":"f0964b6353e0656bef5b38a0d913f49246ca2344","tid":1951113,"uid":171866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T20:05:47.000Z","msg":"自己太樣衰唔敢倒追？<br />\n我比人倒追，但外貌真係引唔起八興趣"},{"pid":"88e0315bfb3c6b919516e271df57e648e234af73","tid":1951113,"uid":158998,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-